Revision history for RPi-Accelerometer-ADXL335

0.01 UNREL
    - Auto generated distribution with Dist::Mgr
    - Added the OO Perl interface; pure Perl, riding on any ADC object
      that provides volts() or percent() (RPi::ADC::ADS and
      RPi::ADC::MCP3008 both work as-is)
    - Added g(), volts(), tilt(), calibrate(), zero_g(), sensitivity()
      and adc()
    - Added hardware-free parameter validation and mocked logic test suites
    - Added examples/gforce.pl and examples/tilt.pl
    - Added the TECHNICAL INFORMATION POD section with the ADXL335
      datasheet specifications, wiring, ratiometric scaling, bandwidth,
      self-test and axis orientation details
